From time to time, one group from the same city appears, but it is much more strange when five or ten groups appear at the same time in the same city.
We are proud and honored to be part of a Seattle group.
I still play with some of them from time to time.
“Last year we were at the festival with Alice in Chains and we were in Canada with Mudhoney, we saw Soundgarden during their tour, so we’re happy to be friends with all of them and it’s an honor for us to be part of the Seattle sound that turned out.
It is also very strange that a group like yours stays together and in the same composition for so long.
